data.description: This property offers a perfect blend of large living space 5 bedrooms, with a den could be used as a sixth bedroom. Location makes this home stand out, its nestled in a wonderful neighborhood with access to local amenities. It's been well-maintained ensuring a move-in-ready experience for the new owners. Natural light floods the home, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.The backyard offers a perfect setting for outdoor gatherings, barbecues, or simply relaxing in your own private oasis. The attached two-car garage provides ample parking and storage space. Enjoy the privacy and added curb appeal of a corner lot, providing more outdoor space and additional parking. Solar and outdoor storage.
